and it didn't quit for four months.

784
00:46:43,661 --> 00:46:47,097
我們經歷了各種各樣的雨…
We've been through every kind of rain there is...

785
00:46:47,165 --> 00:46:49,793
象小針樣的雨
little bitty stinging rain

786
00:46:50,315 --> 00:46:53,524
