828
00:48:35,488 --> 00:48:38,249
只要她有時間
just as soon as she had the time.

829
00:48:38,327 --> 00:48:41,259
我總是告訴她我很平安
I'd always let her know that I was O. K.

830
00:48:41,330 --> 00:48:48,760
