00:54:33,815 --> 00:54:35,836
啊 布巴 不
O-Oh, Bubba, no.

919
00:54:35,919 --> 00:54:37,714
我沒事的
I'll be all right.

920
00:54:46,100 --> 00:54:47,188
行了
Come on.

921
00:54:47,269 --> 00:54:48,995
行了 行了
Come on. Come on.

922
00:54:52,977 --> 00:54:55,671
我沒事 福雷斯
Ugh. I'm O.K., Forrest.

923
00:54:58,620 --> 00:55:00,550
我沒事 我很好
I'm O.K. I'm fine.

924
00:55:37,077 --> 00:55:40,101
炸平那
Top smoke. Get it up there .

925
00:55:40,182 --> 00:55:43,046
如果我知道這將是
If I'd have known this was going to be

926
00:55:43,118 --> 00:55:46,050
我和布巴的最後一次談話
the last time me and Bubba was gonna talk,

927
00:55:46,123 --> 00:55:49,055
我會想些更好的話來說
I'd of thought of something better to say.

928
00:55:49,129 --> 00:55:50,182
嘿 布巴
Hey, Bubba.

929
00:55:50,263 --> 00:55:51,523
嘿 福雷斯
Hey, Forrest.

930
00:55:53,968 --> 00:55:55,398
福雷斯…
Forrest...

931
00:55:55,472 --> 00:55:58,563
出什麼事了？
Why did this happen?

932
00:55:58,643 --> 00:56:01,575
你中彈了
You got shot.

933
00:56:01,645 --> 00:56:06,014
布巴說了一句我永遠不會忘記的話
Then Bubba said something I won't ever forget.

934
00:56:06,086 --> 00:56:09,646
我想回家
I want to go home.

935
00:56:09,726 --> 00:56:12,521
布巴是我最好的好朋友
Bubba was my best good friend.

936
00:56:12,596 --> 00:56:14,526
我還知道
And even I know

937
00:56:14,599 --> 00:56:18,034
好朋友不是那麼容易找到的
that ain't something you can find just around the corner.

938
00:56:18,105 --> 00:56:21,540
布巴想當一個捕蝦船的船長
Bubba was going to be a shrimping boat captain,

939
00:56:21,611 --> 00:56:25,910
但是 他卻死在越南的一條河邊
but instead, he died right there by that river in Vietnam.

940
00:56:31,492 --> 00:56:33,822
我要說的就是這些了
That's all I have to say about that.

941
00:56:36,033 --> 00:56:38,226
那是粒子彈 是嗎？
It was a bullet, wasn't it?

942
00:56:40,139 --> 00:56:41,569
子彈？
A bullet?

943
00:56:41,640 --> 00:56:44,368
跳起來咬你的那個東西
That jumped up and bit you.

944
00:56:45,513 --> 00:56:47,375
啊 對 先生
Oh. Yes, sir.

945
00:56:47,449 --> 00:56:50,075
正好咬在我屁股上
Bit me directly in the but-tocks .

946
00:56:50,152 --> 00:56:54,589
他們說這樣的傷口價值百萬 但…
They said it was a million dollar wound, but...

947
00:56:54,659 --> 00:56:56,589
那些錢大概是被軍隊留著了
the army must keep that money ,

948
00:56:56,662 --> 00:57:00,595
因為那一百萬我至今連半毛錢也沒看見
'cause I still ain't seen a nickel of that million dollars .

949
00:57:00,668 --> 00:57:04,424
屁股受傷的唯一好處
The only good thing about being wounded in the but-tocks

950
00:57:04,562 --> 00:57:06,322
是冰淇淋
is the ice cream.

951
00:57:06,397 --> 00:57:09,295
我能吃多少冰淇淋他們就給我多少
They gave me all the ice cream I could eat.

952
00:57:09,369 --> 00:57:10,799
你猜怎麼著？
And guess what?

953
00:57:10,870 --> 00:57:14,770
我的一位好朋友就在隔壁床上
A good friend of mine was in the bed right next door.

954
00:57:16,080 --> 00:57:19,138
丹中尉 我給你拿冰淇淋來了
Lieutenant Dan, I got you some ice cream.

955
00:57:21,019 --> 00:57:23,747
丹中尉 冰淇淋！
Lieutenant Dan, ice cream!

956
00:57:34,607 --> 00:57:37,368
你該洗澡了 中尉
It's time for your bath, Lieutenant.

957
00:57:45,622 --> 00:57:47,018
哈珀！
Harper!

958
00:57:50,630 --> 00:57:52,060
庫珀
Cooper.

959
00:57:52,131 --> 00:57:53,059
拉森
Larson.

960
00:57:55,136 --> 00:57:56,396
韋斯特
Webster.

961
00:57:57,640 --> 00:57:59,070
阿甘
Gump.

962
00:57:59,142 --> 00:58:00,572
阿甘！
Gump!

963
00:58:00,645 --> 00:58:02,270
我是福雷斯甘
I'm Forrest Gump.

964
00:58:04,583 --> 00:58:05,979
凱利
Kyle.

965
00:58:07,588 --> 00:58:08,917
尼科斯
Nichols.

966
00:58:10,660 --> 00:58:13,024
麥克米爾
McMill.

967
00:58:13,097 --> 00:58:14,081
約翰遜
Johnson.

968
00:58:25,164 --> 00:58:28,130
驚喜 驚喜 驚喜！
Surprise, surprise, surprise!

969
00:58:30,939 --> 00:58:34,374
阿甘 你怎麼能看這種狗屎節目？
Gump, how can you watch that stupid shit?

970
00:58:34,444 --> 00:58:35,874
把它關掉
Turn it off.

971
00:58:35,946 --> 00:58:38,379
你正在收看美軍台
You are tuned to the American forces

972
00:58:38,451 --> 00:58:39,881
越南電視網
Vietnam network.

973
00:58:39,953 --> 00:58:41,509
這是西貢台6頻道
This is channel 6, Saigon.

974
00:58:43,957 --> 00:58:45,615
接得好 阿甘
Good catch, Gump.

975
00:58:47,463 --> 00:58:49,360
你知道怎麼打嗎？
You know how to play this?

976
00:58:50,969 --> 00:58:53,436
來 我教你
Come on. Let me show you.

977
00:58:54,974 --> 00:58:57,407
打乒乓球的關鍵就是
Now, the secret to this game is

978
00:58:57,477 --> 00:58:59,407
無論發生什麼事
no matter what happens,

979
00:58:59,480 --> 00:59:01,913
永遠不要…
never, ever...

980
00:59:01,985 --> 00:59:04,075
把目光離開球
take your eye off the ball.

981
00:59:06,993 --> 00:59:08,253
好吧
All right.

982
00:59:11,500 --> 00:59:12,930
不知為什麼
For some reason,

983
00:59:13,002 --> 00:59:15,435
我天生是打乒乓的料
Ping-Pong came very natural to me.

984
00:59:15,505 --> 00:59:16,663
看見了？
See?

985
00:59:16,740 --> 00:59:18,933
連傻瓜也會打
Any idiot can play .

986
00:59:19,011 --> 00:59:22,446
於是我開始經常打球
So I started playing it all the time.

987
00:59:22,517 --> 00:59:24,142
我打乒乓球
I played Ping-Pong

988
00:59:24,218 --> 00:59:27,812
甚至沒人陪著也能打
even when I didn't have anyone to play Ping-Pong with.

989
00:59:36,169 --> 00:59:37,599
醫院堛漱H
The hospital's people

990
00:59:37,673 --> 00:59:41,606
說我就像下了水的鴨子…
said it made me look like a duck in water...

991
00:59:41,678 --> 00:59:43,108
不管那是什麼意思
Whatever that means.

992
00:59:43,180 --> 00:59:46,409
但連丹中尉也來看我打球
Even Lieutenant Dan would come and watch me play.

993
00:59:51,150 --> 00:59:53,583
我打了這麼多的乒乓球
I played Ping-Pong so much,

994
00:59:53,652 --> 00:59:56,482
連睡覺時也在打
I even played it in my sleep.

995
01:00:03,601 --> 01:00:04,529
現在…
Now...

996
01:00:04,603 --> 01:00:06,033
聽我說
you listen to me.

997
01:00:06,106 --> 01:00:08,036
我們都有自己的命運
We all have a destiny.

998
01:00:08,108 --> 01:00:11,543
沒什麼事是完全偶然的 它總有緣故
Nothing just happens. It's all part of a plan!

999
01:00:11,615 --> 01:00:14,604
我應該和我的士兵一起死在那兒
I should have died out there with my men,

1000
01:00:14,685 --> 01:00:18,676
但現在…我只是個他媽的殘廢人
but now...I'm nothing but a god damn cripple,

1001
01:00:18,757 --> 01:00:20,449
沒腿的怪物！
a legless freak!

1002
01:00:20,526 --> 01:00:22,616
看著我！
Look. Look! Look at me!

1003
01:00:22,697 --> 01:00:24,127
你看見沒有？
You see that?

1004
01:00:24,200 --> 01:00:26,062
你知不知道
Do you know what it's like

1005
01:00:26,136 --> 01:00:29,125
沒有腿是什麼感覺？
not to be able to use your legs?

1006
01:00:31,143 --> 01:00:33,198
是 長官 我知道
Y-Y -Yes, sir, I do.

1007
01:00:36,652 --> 01:00:39,413
你清楚我的話沒有？
Did you hear what I said?

1008
01:00:39,489 --> 01:00:41,351
你害了我！
You cheated me!

1009
01:00:41,425 --> 01:00:42,855
我有自己的命運
I had a destiny .

1010
01:00:42,927 --> 01:00:45,450
我本該死在戰場上
I was supposed to die in the field

1011
01:00:45,530 --> 01:00:46,722
帶著榮譽！
with honor!

1012
01:00:46,799 --> 01:00:48,525
那才是我的命運
That was my destiny,

1013
01:00:48,602 --> 01:00:51,568
而你…使我得不到它！
and you... cheated me out of it!

1014
01:01:00,119 --> 01:01:02,483
你聽明白我的話了嗎 阿甘？
You understand what I'm saying, Gump?

1015
01:01:04,960 --> 01:01:08,051
本來不應該是這樣…
This wasn't supposed to happen...

1016
01:01:08,131 --> 01:01:09,926
我不應該這樣
Not to me.

1017
01:01:11,470 --> 01:01:12,992
我有自己的命運
I had a destiny.

1018
01:01:14,977 --> 01:01:16,567
我曾經是…
I was...

1019
01:01:16,644 --> 01:01:18,404
中尉軍官…
Lieutenant...

1020
01:01:18,481 --> 01:01:20,207
丹泰勒
Dan Taylor.

1021
01:01:25,090 --> 01:01:27,020
你仍然是
Y-You still

1022
01:01:27,093 --> 01:01:28,751
丹中尉
Lieutenant Dan.

1023
01:01:51,129 --> 01:01:52,559
看著我
Look at me.

1024
01:01:54,133 --> 01:01:56,566
現在我能做什麼？
What am I going to do now?

1025
01:01:59,141 --> 01:02:01,936
現在我能做什麼？
What am I going to do now?

1026
01:02:11,661 --> 01:02:13,286
列兵阿甘？
PFC Gump?

1027
01:02:15,166 --> 01:02:16,892
是 長官！
Yes, sir!

1028
01:02:16,968 --> 01:02:18,364
因為你的表現
As you were.

1029
01:02:19,504 --> 01:02:20,592
孩子
Son,

1030
01:02:20,673 --> 01:02:23,131
你獲得榮譽勳章
you been awarded the Medal of Honor.

1031
01:02:23,267 --> 01:02:25,496
你知道嗎 丹中尉？
Guess what, Lieutenant Dan?

1032
01:02:25,570 --> 01:02:28,298
他們要給我勳…
They want to give me a med...

1033
01:02:34,084 --> 01:02:36,014
太太
Ma'am.

1034
01:02:36,087 --> 01:02:38,520
丹中尉怎麼了？
What did they do with Lieutenant Dan?

1035
01:02:38,590 --> 01:02:40,452
他們送他回家了
They sent him home.

1036
01:02:47,102 --> 01:02:50,469
兩星期後 我離開越南
Two weeks later, I left Vietnam.

1037
01:02:50,542 --> 01:02:52,030
典禮已經開始
The ceremony was kicked off

1038
01:02:52,111 --> 01:02:54,201
首先是總統的演說
with a can did speech by the president

1039
01:02:54,281 --> 01:02:58,718
關於擴大越南戰爭的必要性
regarding the need for further escalation of the war in Vietnam.

1040
01:02:58,786 --> 01:03:02,719
約翰遜總統給四名軍人頒發了榮譽勳章
Johnson awarded 4 Medals of Honor to men from each of the armed services.

1041
01:03:02,793 --> 01:03:04,690
美國深深地感謝你 孩子
America owes you a debt of gratitude, son.

1042
01:03:06,633 --> 01:03:08,563
我知道你受過傷
I understand you were wounded.

1043
01:03:08,634 --> 01:03:10,564
你的傷口在哪兒？
Where were you hit?

1044
01:03:10,639 --> 01:03:12,229
在屁股上 先生
In the but-tocks, sir.

1045
01:03:12,307 --> 01:03:14,237
嗯 那一定很好看
Well, that must be a sight.

1046
01:03:14,310 --> 01:03:17,071
我倒想瞧一瞧
I'd kinda like to see that.

1047
01:03:17,149 --> 01:03:20,913
「我獻歌給你 羅賓森太太」
# And here's to you, Mrs. Robinson #

1048
01:03:20,988 --> 01:03:24,046
「耶穌對你也特別垂青」
#Jesus loves you more than you will know #

1049
01:03:27,697 --> 01:03:31,029
「上帝保佑你 羅賓森太太」
# God bless you, please, Mrs. Robinson #

1050
01:03:31,103 --> 01:03:32,761
老天 這孩子！
God damn, son!

1051
01:03:34,608 --> 01:03:38,043
然後媽媽回酒店休息
After that, Mama went to the hotel to lay down,

1052
01:03:38,113 --> 01:03:42,046
我出去在我們的首都隨處走走
so I went out for a walk to see our nation's capital.

1053
01:03:42,119 --> 01:03:44,049
希拉堙I我找了獸醫來
Hilary! I got the vets.

1054
01:03:44,122 --> 01:03:46,917
你找他們做什麼？
What do you want to do with them?

1055
01:03:46,993 --> 01:03:49,500
媽媽就應該休息
It's a good thing Mama was resting,

1056
01:03:49,500 --> 01:03:52,000
因為街上人擠得要死
'cause the streets was awful crowded with people

1057
01:03:52,000 --> 01:03:54,563
他們來看那些雕像和紀念碑
lookin'at all the statues and monuments,

1058
01:03:54,639 --> 01:03:58,571
有些人吵吵嚷嚷的
and some of them people were loud and pushy.

1059
01:03:58,578 --> 01:04:00,166
好了 跟著我！
O.K., follow me!

1060
01:04:00,242 --> 01:04:03,540
不管去哪 我都要排隊
Everywhere I went, I had to stand in line.

1061
01:04:10,356 --> 01:04:11,409
快點
Come on.

1062
01:04:11,490 --> 01:04:12,474
走！
Go!

1063
01:04:21,371 --> 01:04:24,738
嘿 你這麼做太對了
Hey, you're a good man for doing this.

1064
01:04:24,738 --> 01:04:26,100
很好
Good.

1065
01:04:26,438 --> 01:04:27,926
好
O.K.

1066
01:04:29,138 --> 01:04:31,770
那兒有這麼個人在演講
There was this man giving a little talk.

1067
01:04:31,783 --> 01:04:33,213
不知什麼原因
And for some reason,

1068
01:04:33,646 --> 01:04:35,578
他身上穿著美國國旗
he was wearing an American flag for a shirt.

1069
01:04:37,151 --> 01:04:41,084
他還很愛說「操」…
And he liked to say the "F" word...a lot.

1070
01:04:41,157 --> 01:04:43,419
操這個、操那個
"F" this and "F" that.

1071
01:04:43,494 --> 01:04:46,460
每次他說「操」
And every time he said the "F" word,

1072
01:04:46,532 --> 01:04:49,590
人們不知什麼原因就一陣歡呼
people, for some reason, well, they cheered.

1073
01:04:51,171 --> 01:04:53,831
對！對！
Yeah! Yeah!

1074
01:04:55,311 --> 01:04:58,369
來 兄弟 上來 兄弟
Come on, man. Come up here, man.

1075
01:04:58,838 --> 01:05:00,200
過來 過來
Come on. Come on.

1076
01:05:00,275 --> 01:05:02,434
對 你！過來 快！
Yeah, you! Come on. Move, move !

1077
01:05:04,079 --> 01:05:06,043
快 我們上去
Go on. Let's get up there .

1078
01:05:19,100 --> 01:05:20,600
給我們講講這場戰爭吧 兄弟
Tell us a little bit about the war, man.

1079
01:05:21,600 --> 01:05:22,440
越南的戰爭？
The war in Vietnam?

1080
01:05:22,487 --> 01:05:25,001
就是這場…
The war in Viet...

1081
01:05:25,100 --> 01:05:27,600
…操他媽的越南戰爭！
fucking-nam!

1082
01:05:51,986 --> 01:05:53,416
嗯…
Well...

1083
01:05:53,489 --> 01:05:56,421
我能說的只有一件事
There was only one thing I could say

1084
01:05:56,495 --> 01:05:57,925
關於越南戰爭
about the war in Vietnam.

1085
01:05:57,996 --> 01:06:00,928
我能說的只有一件事關於…
There's only one thing I can say about...

1086
01:06:01,000 --> 01:06:02,488
越南戰爭
the war in Vietnam.

1087
01:06:05,007 --> 01:06:07,869
在越南…
In Vietnam...

1088
01:06:19,028 --> 01:06:20,958
你在幹什麼…
What the hell are you do...

1089
01:06:21,031 --> 01:06:23,963
我打死你 你這該死的豬頭！
I'll beat your head in, you goddamn oinker!

1090
01:06:24,035 --> 01:06:26,468
天那！他究竟是怎麼搞的？
Jesus Christ! What did they do with this?

1091
01:06:26,540 --> 01:06:28,504
聽不見！
Can't hear you!

1092
01:06:30,144 --> 01:06:32,406
什麼也聽不見
Can't hear anything!

1093
01:06:33,483 --> 01:06:34,411
這個…這個！
This...This one!

1094
01:06:34,484 --> 01:06:35,412
給我那個！
Give me that!

1095
01:06:35,485 --> 01:06:38,043
大聲點！
Speak up!

1096
01:06:40,259 --> 01:06:41,623
我要說的就是…
And that's all I have to say

1097
01:06:41,623 --> 01:06:42,223
這些
about that.

1098
01:06:48,973 --> 01:06:51,166
說得很好 兄弟
That's so right on, man.

1099
01:06:51,244 --> 01:06:52,709
你說得很好
You said it all.

1100
01:06:54,247 --> 01:06:56,406
你叫什麼名字 兄弟？
What's your name, man?

1101
01:06:56,485 --> 01:06:59,920
我叫福雷斯 福雷斯甘
My name is Forrest. Forrest Gump.

1102
01:07:00,623 --> 01:07:02,179
福雷斯甘
Forrest Gump.

1103
01:07:02,253 --> 01:07:02,886
阿甘! 阿甘!
- Gump! Gump! - Gump!

1104
01:07:04,498 --> 01:07:06,463
福雷斯！
Forrest!

1105
01:07:07,538 --> 01:07:08,969
福雷斯！
