I will miss you, Forrest.

1645
01:41:12,076 --> 01:41:14,340
她得了癌癥
She had got the cancer

1646
01:41:14,411 --> 01:41:16,345
在星期二去世了
and died on a Tuesday.

1647
01:41:16,414 --> 01:41:19,008
我給她買了頂新帽子
I bought her a new hat

1648
01:41:19,084 --> 01:41:21,109
上面有很多小花
with little flowers on it.

1649
01:41:24,056 --> 01:41:26,752
我要說的說是這麼多了
And that's all I have to say about that.

1650
01:41:34,035 --> 01:41:36,731
你不是說你在等7路車嗎？
Didn't you say you were waiting for the number 7 bus?

1651
01:41:36,804 --> 01:41:39,534
等一下還會有下一班車的
There'll be another one along shortly.

1652
01:41:43,045 --> 01:41:47,482
現在因為我成了足球明星和戰爭英雄
Now, because I had been a football star and war hero

1653
01:41:47,551 --> 01:41:50,486
以及全國知名的人物和捕蝦船的船長
and national celebrity and a shrimping boat captain

1654
01:41:50,554 --> 01:41:51,987
以及大學畢業生
and a college graduate,

1655
01:41:52,056 --> 01:41:54,490
亞拉巴馬州綠茵鎮的父老鄉親
the city fathers of Greenbow, Alabama,

1656
01:41:54,559 --> 01:41:57,050
決定給我一個好工作
decided to get together and offered me a fine job.

1657
01:41:58,564 --> 01:42:02,091
所以我不再回去和丹中尉一起工作了
So I never went back to work for Lieutenant Dan,

1658
01:42:02,167 --> 01:42:05,102
但他繼續打理著我們布巴甘公司的財產
though he did take care of my Bubba Gump money.

1659
01:42:05,171 --> 01:42:08,106
他替我買了一家賣蘋果的公司的股票
He got me invested in some kind of fruit company.

1660
01:42:08,174 --> 01:42:10,608
後有他打電話給我
So then I got a call from him

1661
01:42:10,678 --> 01:42:13,238
說我們再也不用擔心沒錢花了
saying we don't have to worry about money no more,

1662
01:42:13,314 --> 01:42:17,717
我說：「好啊 又少一件麻煩事」
and I said, "That's good. One less thing."

1663
01:42:17,786 --> 01:42:19,583
「我有了新的希望…」
# I've got a new hope... #

1664
01:42:19,654 --> 01:42:22,088
媽媽說過財產不用太多
Now Mama said there's only so much fortune

1665
01:42:22,158 --> 01:42:23,785
一個人用不了多少
a man really needs,

1666
01:42:23,859 --> 01:42:27,260
多餘的錢只是用來炫耀
and the rest is just for showing off.

1667
01:42:27,330 --> 01:42:30,231
所以我拿出一大堆
So I gave a whole bunch of it

1668
01:42:30,300 --> 01:42:33,565
給四方福音教堂…
to the Four square Gospel Church...

1669
01:42:33,637 --> 01:42:38,700
又拿出一大堆給拉巴特灣漁場醫院…
and I gave a whole bunch to the Bayou La Batre Fishing Hospital...

1670
01:42:40,179 --> 01:42:42,613
雖然布巴已經死了
and even though Bubba was dead

1671
01:42:42,681 --> 01:42:46,117
丹中尉也說我是笨蛋
and Lieutenant Dan said I was nuts,

1672
01:42:46,186 --> 01:42:48,916
我還是把布巴那一份給了布巴的媽媽
I gave Bubba's mama Bubba's share.

1673
01:42:52,293 --> 01:42:53,954
你猜怎麼著？
You know what?

1674
01:42:54,028 --> 01:42:57,964
她再也不用去任何人家的廚房幹活了
She didn't have to work in nobody's kitchen no more.

1675
01:42:58,032 --> 01:43:00,626
那感覺真不錯
That smells wonderful.

1676
01:43:00,702 --> 01:43:03,136
因為我成了億萬富翁
And 'cause I was a gozillionaire

1677
01:43:03,205 --> 01:43:06,140
並且我喜歡幹活
and I liked doing it so much,

1678
01:43:06,209 --> 01:43:09,645
我免費幫他們割草
I cut that grass for free.

1679
01:43:11,081 --> 01:43:14,517
但到了晚上無事可幹
But at night time when there was nothing to do

1680
01:43:14,585 --> 01:43:17,019
房子空空蕩蕩的
and the house was all empty,

1681
01:43:17,088 --> 01:43:20,023
我會經常想念珍妮
I'd always think of Jenny.

1682
01:44:23,539 --> 01:44:27,339
然後…她就出現了
And then...she was there.

1683
01:45:00,114 --> 01:45:01,411
你好 福雷斯
Hello, Forrest.

1684
01:45:01,483 --> 01:45:03,678
你好 珍妮
Hello, Jenny .

1685
01:45:14,531 --> 01:45:17,659
珍妮回來與我一起住
Jenny came back and stayed with me.

1686
01:45:17,735 --> 01:45:22,570
也許因為她沒什麼別的地方可去了
Maybe it was because she had no where else to go,

1687
01:45:22,640 --> 01:45:26,007
也許因為她太累了
or maybe it was because she was so tired

1688
01:45:26,078 --> 01:45:29,514
因為她總是在睡覺
'cause she went to bed and slept and slept

1689
01:45:29,582 --> 01:45:31,812
好像她多年沒睡覺了
like she hadn't slept in years.

1690
01:45:31,885 --> 01:45:34,251
有她在家真好
It was wonderful having her home.

1691
01:45:34,320 --> 01:45:36,754
每天我們都散步
Every day we'd take a walk,

1692
01:45:36,824 --> 01:45:40,760
我不停地跟她說話
and I'd jabber on like a monkey in a tree,

1693
01:45:40,829 --> 01:45:43,764
她聽我說乒乓球和捕蝦
and she'd listen about Ping-Ponging and shrimping

1694
01:45:43,832 --> 01:45:46,767
還有媽媽去天堂的事
and Mama making a trip up to heaven.

1695
01:45:46,836 --> 01:45:48,770
我不停地說
I did all the talking.

1696
01:45:48,838 --> 01:45:51,329
珍妮總是很安靜
Jenny most of the time was real quiet.

1697
01:46:30,987 --> 01:46:33,717
你怎麼能這麼做？
How could you do this?

1698
01:47:11,033 --> 01:47:15,527
有時我想石頭會不夠用
Sometimes I guess there just aren't enough rocks.

1699
01:47:17,040 --> 01:47:19,975
我一直不知道她為什麼回來
I never really knew why she came back,

1700
01:47:20,044 --> 01:47:21,477
但我不介意
but I didn't care.

1701
01:47:21,545 --> 01:47:23,479
就像昔日重來
It was like olden times.

1702
01:47:23,548 --> 01:47:26,346
我們又形影不離了
We was like peas and carrots again.

1703
01:47:27,986 --> 01:47:30,420
每天我都會採來好看的花
Every day, I'd pick pretty flowers

1704
01:47:30,490 --> 01:47:34,051
放在她的房間
and put them in her room for her,

1705
01:47:34,127 --> 01:47:37,563
而她給了我人所能得到的最好的禮物
and she gave me the best gift anyone could ever get

1706
01:47:37,631 --> 01:47:39,064
在整個世界
in the wide world.

1707
01:47:39,133 --> 01:47:41,658
這是最適合跑步的
They're made just for running.

1708
01:47:41,736 --> 01:47:42,998
「帶我回家見親朋」
# Carry me home to see my kin #

1709
01:47:45,674 --> 01:47:48,199
他還教我如何跳舞
And she even showed me how to dance.

1710
01:47:50,046 --> 01:47:52,412
「我又想起老朋友」
#I miss ol'Bammy once again #

1711
01:47:52,481 --> 01:47:53,709
「我不再對他不起」
#And I think it's a sin #

1712
01:47:54,985 --> 01:47:56,646
「亞拉巴馬我的家…」
# Sweet home Alabama... #

1713
01:47:56,720 --> 01:48:01,748
我們就像一家人 珍妮和我…
Well, we was like family, Jenny and me...

1714
01:48:04,662 --> 01:48:07,859
那是我一生最快樂的時光
and it was the happiest time in my life.

1715
01:48:32,061 --> 01:48:33,494
你看還要看嗎？
You done watching it?

1716
01:48:34,564 --> 01:48:36,555
我要去睡了
I'm going to bed.

1717
01:48:47,447 --> 01:48:49,005
你能嫁給我嗎？
Will you marry me?

1718
01:48:54,056 --> 01:48:57,025
我會做個好丈夫的 珍妮
I'd make a good husband, Jenny.

1719
01:48:59,561 --> 01:49:01,461
你會的 福雷斯
You would, Forrest.

1720
01:49:03,900 --> 01:49:05,663
但你不能嫁給我
But you won't marry me.

1721
01:49:08,072 --> 01:49:10,472
你不願意嫁給我
You don't want to marry me.

1722
01:49:13,578 --> 01:49:15,978
你為什麼不愛我 珍妮？
Why don't you love me, Jenny?

1723
01:49:21,420 --> 01:49:23,354
我不是很聰明
I'm not a smart man,

1724
01:49:23,422 --> 01:49:27,882
但我知道什麼是愛
but I know what love is.

1725
01:50:04,804 --> 01:50:06,066
珍妮…
Jenny...

1726
01:50:08,142 --> 01:50:10,440
福雷斯 我真的愛你
Forrest, I do love you.

1727
01:51:03,472 --> 01:51:06,066
那你為什麼要跑？
Where are you running off to?

1728
01:51:06,143 --> 01:51:07,701
我沒有跑
I'm not running.

1729
01:52:38,135 --> 01:52:40,103
那一天
That day,

1730
01:52:40,170 --> 01:52:41,603
不知什麼原因
for no particular reason,

1731
01:52:41,672 --> 01:52:44,664
我決定出去跑一趟
I decided to go for a little run.

1732
01:52:44,741 --> 01:52:48,199
所以我跑到路的盡頭
So I ran to the end of the road,

1733
01:52:48,279 --> 01:52:51,612
當我到達那 我想也許我能跑到城邊
and when I got there, I thought maybe I'd run to the end of town.

1734
01:52:51,683 --> 01:52:54,311
卡特總統因中暑病倒…
President Carter, suffering from heat exhaustion...

1735
01:52:54,385 --> 01:52:56,376
而當我到達那
And when I got there,

1736
01:52:56,454 --> 01:53:00,390
我想也許我能跑遍綠茵縣
I thought maybe I'd just run across Greenbow County.

1737
01:53:00,459 --> 01:53:02,893
這時我想既然我跑了那麼遠
Now, I figured since I'd run this far,

1738
01:53:02,961 --> 01:53:06,829
也許我可以跑遍亞拉巴馬州
maybe I'd just run across the great state of Alabama.

1739
01:53:06,899 --> 01:53:08,833
我就這麼做了
And that's what I did.

1740
01:53:08,902 --> 01:53:10,893
我橫越整個亞拉巴馬
I ran clear across Alabama.

1741
01:53:10,970 --> 01:53:15,498
不知什麼原因 我繼續跑
No particular reason. I just kept on going.

1742
01:53:15,575 --> 01:53:17,509
我一直跑到大海
I ran clear to the ocean.

1743
01:53:22,750 --> 01:53:24,342
當我到達那
And when I got there,

1744
01:53:24,418 --> 01:53:26,852
我想既然我跑了那麼遠
I figured since I'd gone this far,

1745
01:53:26,921 --> 01:53:30,084
也許不如掉頭繼續跑
might as well turn around, just keep on going.

1746
01:53:32,127 --> 01:53:35,187
然後當我跑到另一個大海
And when I got to another ocean,

1747
01:53:35,263 --> 01:53:38,198
我想既然我跑了那麼遠…
I figured since I'd gone this far...

1748
01:53:40,103 --> 01:53:42,401
我也許不如掉頭
I might as well just turn back

1749
01:53:42,472 --> 01:53:44,064
繼續跑下去
and keep right on going.

1750
01:53:44,140 --> 01:53:47,473
當我累了 我就睡覺
when I got tired, I slept.

1751
01:53:47,544 --> 01:53:49,637
當我餓了 我就吃飯
when I got hungry, I ate.

1752
01:53:49,713 --> 01:53:52,147
當我想去…
When I had to go...

1753
01:53:52,216 --> 01:53:53,240
你知道…
you know...

1754
01:53:54,385 --> 01:53:55,545
我就去
I went.

1755
01:53:55,619 --> 01:53:56,813
所以…
And so...

1756
01:53:56,888 --> 01:53:58,913
你不停地跑?
you just ran?

1757
01:54:00,558 --> 01:54:02,116
對
Yeah.

1758
01:54:02,193 --> 01:54:05,890
「看著路在車輪下延伸」
# Lookin' out at the road rushin' under my wheels #

1759
01:54:09,068 --> 01:54:11,935
「看著一年年時光飛逝」
# Lookin' back at the years gone by #

1760
01:54:12,004 --> 01:54:14,302
「就像一片片夏日農田」
# Like so many summer fields #

1761
01:54:15,909 --> 01:54:19,140
「六五年那時我十七歲」
# In '65, I was 17 #

1762
01:54:19,212 --> 01:54:21,646
「我在一刻不停地奔跑」
# And runnin' up one on one #

1763
01:54:23,083 --> 01:54:25,677
「我不知道跑到了何處」
# I don't know where I'm runnin' now #

1764
01:54:25,753 --> 01:54:28,847
「我只是在不停地奔跑」
# I'm just runnin' on #

1765
01:54:28,923 --> 01:54:30,686
「奔跑」
# Runnin' on #

1766
01:54:30,758 --> 01:54:32,692
「無緣無故地奔跑」
# Runnin' on empty #

1767
01:54:32,760 --> 01:54:34,159
「奔跑」
# Runnin' on #

1768
01:54:34,228 --> 01:54:36,025
「精疲力竭」
# Runnin' dry #

1769
01:54:36,098 --> 01:54:37,030
「奔跑…」
# Runnin' on... #

1770
01:54:37,099 --> 01:54:38,691
我想了很多事…
I'd think a lot...

1771
01:54:38,767 --> 01:54:43,033
關於媽媽和布巴還有丹中尉
about Mama and Bubba and Lieutenant Dan.

1772
01:54:43,105 --> 01:54:44,629
但最經常的
But most of all,

1773
01:54:44,706 --> 01:54:46,697
我在想念珍妮
I thought about Jenny.

1774
01:54:46,776 --> 01:54:49,540
我非常想念她
I thought about her a lot.

1775
01:54:51,014 --> 01:54:52,606
兩年多來
For more than two years,

1776
01:54:52,682 --> 01:54:54,411
一位名叫福雷斯甘的人
a man named Forrest Gump,

1777
01:54:54,484 --> 01:54:57,476
來自亞拉巴馬綠茵縣的園藝師 除了睡覺
a gardener from Greenbow, Alabama, stopping only to sleep,

1778
01:54:57,555 --> 01:54:59,819
就是不停跑步橫越美國
has been running across America.

1779
01:54:59,890 --> 01:55:01,983
查爾斯庫珀為你報導
Charles Cooper brings you this report.

1780
01:55:02,059 --> 01:55:03,321
他這是第四次
For the fourth time

1781
01:55:03,394 --> 01:55:04,986
進行橫越美國的旅程
on his journey across America,

1782
01:55:05,063 --> 01:55:07,497
福雷斯甘 來自亞拉巴馬綠茵縣的園藝師
Forrest Gump, the gardener from Greenbow, Alabama,

1783
01:55:07,566 --> 01:55:10,330
今天將再次跑過密西西比河
is about to cross the Mississippi River again today.

1784
01:55:10,402 --> 01:55:11,835
天那 福雷斯？
I'll be damned. Forrest?

1785
01:55:11,903 --> 01:55:13,837
先生 你為什麼要跑？
Sir, where are you running?

1786
01:55:13,905 --> 01:55:16,339
你是為了世界和平嗎？
Are you doing this for world peace?

1787
01:55:16,409 --> 01:55:18,843
你是為了無家可者嗎？
Are you doing this for the homeless?

1788
01:55:18,911 --> 01:55:20,845
你是為了婦女權利嗎？
Are you running for women's rights?

1789
01:55:20,913 --> 01:55:21,845
為了保護環境嗎？
The environment?

1790
01:55:21,914 --> 01:55:23,176
他們就是不相信
they just couldn't believe

1791
01:55:23,249 --> 01:55:25,683
有些人跑步
that Somebody would do all that running

1792
01:55:25,752 --> 01:55:27,185
什麼都不為
for no particular reason.

1793
01:55:27,254 --> 01:55:28,846
你為什麼這樣做？
Why are you doing this?

1794
01:55:28,922 --> 01:55:31,186
我只是想跑
I just felt like running.

1795
01:55:31,258 --> 01:55:32,885
我只是想跑
I just felt like runnin'.

1796
01:55:33,962 --> 01:55:34,894
是你
That's you.

1797
01:55:34,963 --> 01:55:37,557
我不敢相信真的是你
I can't believe it's really you.

1798
01:55:37,632 --> 01:55:39,065
然後…不知什麼原因
Now...for some reason,

1799
01:55:39,133 --> 01:55:41,567
我所做的事好像
what I was doing seemed to...

1800
01:55:41,636 --> 01:55:43,160
在某些人看來有了意義
make sense to people.

1801
01:55:43,238 --> 01:55:46,173
我的頭腦中好像響起一聲警報
It was like an alarm went off in my head.

1802
01:55:46,242 --> 01:55:49,268
我說 「他是個實幹家 
I said, "Here's a guy that's got his act together.

1803
01:55:49,345 --> 01:55:51,279
他擁有所有問題的答案」
Here's somebody who has the answer."

1804
01:55:51,347 --> 01:55:53,281
我要追隨你 甘先生
I'll follow you anywhere, Mr. Gump.

1805
01:55:53,350 --> 01:55:55,682
於是我有了夥伴
So I got company.

1806
01:55:57,220 --> 01:55:59,780
然後 我有了更多的夥伴
And after that, I got more company.

1807
01:55:59,856 --> 01:56:03,383
然後 又有更多的人加入
And then, even more people joined in.

1808
01:56:05,396 --> 01:56:07,077
有人後來告訴我
Somebody later told me

1809
01:56:07,210 --> 01:56:08,768
人們看到了希望
it gave people hope.

1810
01:56:10,347 --> 01:56:11,507
那時…
Now...

1811
01:56:11,581 --> 01:56:14,072
那時我什麼也不知道
Now, I don't know anything about that,

1812
01:56:14,151 --> 01:56:16,585
有些人曾經問我
but some of those people asked me

1813
01:56:16,654 --> 01:56:18,588
我能不能幫助他們
if I could help them out.

1814
01:56:18,656 --> 01:56:21,090
我想你也許能夠幫助我
I was wondering if you might help me.

1815
01:56:21,158 --> 01:56:23,092
我是做貼紙生意的
I'm in the bumper sticker business.

1816
01:56:23,161 --> 01:56:24,753
我需要一句好的口號
I need a good slogan,

1817
01:56:24,830 --> 01:56:26,764
你很有天才
and since you've been so inspirational,

1818
01:56:26,832 --> 01:56:29,426
我想你也許能幫助我…
I thought you might be able to help me...

1819
01:56:29,501 --> 01:56:31,264
啊！你剛跑過…
Whoa, man! You just ran

1820
01:56:31,336 --> 01:56:33,634
一大堆狗屎！
through a big pile of dog shit!

1821
